<div id="article" class="article-new">
    <h1>Debate the monarchy's future (but nothing will change)</h1>
	</em>
</p>
<p class="tagline">'It is safer to allow one well-known family, however dysfunctional, provide heads of state'</p>
	<p class="author">
            <author>
					By Andreas Whittam Smith</author><br/>
            </p>

		<div class="clear-o">
			<p class="info"><em>Monday, 11 December 2000</em></p>

			<ul class="article-tools">
